About Chris

Chris Wilson is a comedian from Greenville, SC. Chris has Cerebral Palsy, but he's not afraid to joke about it. It's better to be laughed with and not laughed at (Chris hopes you do laugh at him hes a comedian).

Hes shared the stage with platinum-selling rapper T.I., sold-out shows with Preacher Lawson (Americas Got Talent), featured for Sam Miller on his 2025 tour, and performed with Dont Tell Comedy.

Chris has a comedy album, Whats Wrong With Your Ass?, available on Bandcamp.

He is a three-time winner of Funny or Fired at The Comedy Zone Greenville.

Chris takes life, disability, and awkward human moments and flips them into sharp, light-hearted comedy.
